    <title>Oracle安装教程</title>
    <url>/2022/02/18/Oracle%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>​        本文将介绍<code>Oracle 11g</code>   在Windows、Docker下安装方法。</p>
<h1><span id="windows">Windows</span></h1><p>​        <code>Windows</code>下安装<code>Oracle</code>比较简单，下载地址为:<a href="https://www.oracle.com/cn/database/technologies/microsoft-windows.html%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BD%E4%B8%A4%E4%B8%AA%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E5%8C%85%E5%90%8E%EF%BC%8C%E6%94%BE%E5%85%A5%E5%90%8C%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E5%A4%B9%E5%90%8E%E7%82%B9%E5%87%BB%60setup.exe%60%EF%BC%8C%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E3%80%82">https://www.oracle.com/cn/database/technologies/microsoft-windows.html，下载两个安装包后，放入同一个文件夹后点击`setup.exe`，进行安装。</a></p>
<p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/TerryLee77/blog_img/img/image-20220225093813064.png" alt="setup"></p>
<p>​            其他安装过程比较简单，不做说明，网上教程也比较丰富，比如<a href="https://www.cnblogs.com/liuhongfeng/p/5267549.html%E7%AD%89%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E3%80%82">https://www.cnblogs.com/liuhongfeng/p/5267549.html等博客。</a></p>
<h1><span id="docker">Docker</span></h1><p>​        下面介绍在windows环境下使用<code>Docker</code>安装<code>Oracle11g</code>。</p>
<ol>
<li><p>确保自己电脑为<strong>windows专业版</strong>，这样才能打开开启windows自带的<strong>Hyer-V</strong>功能。</p>
</li>
<li><p>随后打开<strong>Hyper-V</strong>功能，具体路径为控制面板 $\rightarrow$程序$\rightarrow$程序和功能，也可以直接在开始界面搜索程序和功能打开，开启<strong>Hyper-V</strong>功能。。</p>
<p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/TerryLee77/blog_img/img/image-20220225094900898.png" alt="image-20220225094900898"></p>
</li>
</ol>
<p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/TerryLee77/blog_img/img/image-20220225094926077.png" alt="image-20220225094926077"></p>
<p>​        </p>
<ol start="3">
<li>前往<a href="https://www.docker.com/products/docker-desktop"><strong>Docker</strong>官网</a>下载Docker for windows客户端，并进行安装</li>
<li>打开<code>终端</code>或者<code>Powershell</code>，<code>cmd</code>输入</li>
</ol>
<figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">docker search oracle</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>

<p>​        查找oracle镜像</p>
<p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/TerryLee77/blog_img/img/image-20220225095444499.png" alt="image-20220225095444499"></p>
<ol start="5">
<li>网上教程均是推荐安装第二个<code>jaspeen/oracle-11g</code>，但是这是基于<code>Centos6.5</code>系统搭建的，而该系统已于2020年停止服务，无法更新，会对后续安装带来一定不便，此处我们安装第一个，输入命令拉去镜像</li>
</ol>
<figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">docker pull wnameless/oracle<span class="literal">-xe</span><span class="literal">-11g</span><span class="literal">-r2</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>

<ol start="6">
<li>输入命令查看已经安装好的镜像</li>
</ol>
<p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/TerryLee77/blog_img/img/image-20220225100038719.png" alt="image-20220225100038719"></p>
<ol start="7">
<li>启动容器，并重命名，将1521端口映射至本机的1521端口</li>
</ol>
<figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">docker run <span class="literal">-d</span> <span class="literal">-p</span> <span class="number">1522</span>:<span class="number">22</span> <span class="literal">-p</span> <span class="number">1521</span>:<span class="number">1521</span> -<span class="literal">-name</span> oracle11gr2 wnameless/oracle<span class="literal">-xe</span><span class="literal">-11g</span><span class="literal">-r2</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>

<ol start="8">
<li>开机</li>
</ol>
<figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">docker <span class="built_in">start</span> oracle11gr2</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>

<ol start="9">
<li>因为18.04版本后移除了ssh功能，此处需要用<code>exec</code>命令进入容器配置</li>
</ol>
<figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">docker exec <span class="literal">-it</span> oracle11gr2 bash</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>

<ol start="10">
<li>进入oracle服务</li>
</ol>
<figure class="highlight shell"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sqlplus /nolog</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>

<p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/TerryLee77/blog_img/img/image-20220225100731354.png" alt="image-20220225100731354"></p>
<ol start="11">
<li><p>在本容器中，<code>sys</code>和<code>system</code>的口令均为<code>oracle</code></p>
</li>
<li><p>尝试进入<code>sys</code>用户</p>
</li>
</ol>
<p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/TerryLee77/blog_img/img/image-20220225100911180.png" alt="image-20220225100911180"></p>
<p>安装过程已经结束，如果想关闭容器，在命令行输入即可</p>
<figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">docker <span class="built_in">kill</span> oracle11gr2</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>

<h1><span id="参考">参考</span></h1><ul>
<li>[1] <a href="https://github.com/wnameless/docker-oracle-xe-11g">https://github.com/wnameless/docker-oracle-xe-11g</a></li>
</ul>
]]></content>
